track_notes: This is not the easiest route. No trails, very rocky. Best option is from Bitedalsdammen.

Toll road, 100 NOK pr. 2023.
Path startes close to red garage/company. Track starts at recommended parking place, close to path start. The path is very good for a long while, and is easy to follow until you get higher up in the mountain. 

**Please note, do not park on the grass spots close to the cabins on the left side of road, as they are private. I was told to move my car during last activation. So drive to a bit larger spot with some construction materials etc, and park on the edge there.

When arriving higher up in the mountain the path is on and off. But the GPS track is now showing the best direct route, so stick to that and you will be fine.

(Edit: Updated GPS-track in 2023)
